    <h1>Best Time to Take Probiotics: The Evidence-Based Guide</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">Should you take probiotics in the morning or at night? With food or on an empty stomach? The answer depends on the specific strain you are taking. We analyzed the clinical research on probiotic survival rates, stomach acid pH patterns, and strain-specific timing to give you a definitive, science-backed protocol.</p>
